Pricegrabber

Parse various infomation (such as item names/price...etc) from sri lankan computer seller's price lists / product catalogs / shopping applications online.

You can configure what parsers are run by modifing the main.rb file. main.rb can be run using the command line and it would print all its output to the screen.

Retailers Supported

abc_computers
barclays
laptoplk
memory_lk
slmega
tech_ware_house

WARNING!!!
running this script(s) continusly against any site could put a hevy strain on the web site. So be mindful of how frequntly you use it.
